Lotka–Volterra Observation Dashboard

A project exploring predator–prey dynamics using real-world population data and mathematical modeling.

What this project will explore

  • Predator and prey population trends over time
  • Phase-plane relationships between species
  • Lotka–Volterra model simulations
  • Comparisons between theory and real data
